  "texts": [
    "Notably, the SFT models for DPO and ADPO were trained independently, referred to as SFT with non-toxic dataset and SFT with toxic dataset, respectively.",
    "Every SFT models are trained for 2 epochs.",
    "For ADPO training, we incorporated an additional dataset BAD for the SFT phase appending a toxic control token to each dialogue.",
    "In generating preference data, we used the unused portion of the Anthropic dataset, excluding the model's final response in each dialogue.",
    "The details of this phase are explained in Section 4.2."
  ],
